main event: A UFO was sighted near Blue Mound, Illinois on September 17, 1955, described as alternating colors and bobbing in the sky.
interesting points: The object alternated between green, blue, red, and white colors,It was perceived to be very high in the sky,The sighting lasted for 30 seconds,12 confirmed witnesses including a dentist claimed to have seen it,There were conflicting conclusions about the sighting, suggesting it could be a balloon, aircraft, or astronomical body.
sighted object: a single object resembling a star
